### Variables
@host = http://localhost:8080
@email = moko@example.com

### ============================================
### AUTH
### ============================================

### Send magic link
POST {{host}}/api/auth/magic-link
Content-Type: application/json

{"email": "{{email}}"}

### Verify magic link (paste token from DB or logs)
# @name verify
GET {{host}}/api/auth/verify?token=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJtb2tvQGV4YW1wbGUuY29tIiwianRpIjoiNmU0MDRhM2ItZjg4OS00MmRlLWI1NjUtNTkxNjBkMWRiNmZkIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc3ODMzOTQ0LCJleHAiOjE3Nzc4MzQ4NDR9.p6cGD_bWdjy8Mawt_diYbACjcaJOSPPtdOXJKkuHavI

### Get current user (needs session cookie from verify response)
GET {{host}}/api/auth/me
Cookie: session={{verify.response.headers.Set-Cookie}}

### Logout
POST {{host}}/api/auth/logout
Cookie: session={{verify.response.headers.Set-Cookie}}

### ============================================
### SYNC
### ============================================

